            <a href="/en/dep/krd/press/press-releases/2010/More-rental-housing-for-people-in-difficulties.html?id=604481" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/upload/KRD/Ingresssbilder/ung_gutt_ingress.jpg" alt="Young man" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/krd/press/press-releases/2010/More-rental-housing-for-people-in-difficulties.html?id=604481" title="">
                        More rental housing for people in difficulties
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development, 11.05.2010]</p>
                <p>“A lot of people have applied for funding in order to set up rental housing this year. We are increasing funding for rental housing by NOK 88.8 million in 2010 in a revised national budget. This means that Husbanken (The Norwegian State Housing Bank) can provide funding for around 1150 homes this year,” says Liv Signe Navarsete, Minister of Local Government and Regional Development.   </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp546192885_wp1648794796_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl00_Label1"></span>                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            <a href="/en/dep/krd/press/press-releases/2010/New-rental-funding-for-regulated-housing-tenants-in-Trondheim.html?id=604480" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/upload/KRD/Ingresssbilder/BOBY/hus1_100x75.jpg" alt="Houses" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/krd/press/press-releases/2010/New-rental-funding-for-regulated-housing-tenants-in-Trondheim.html?id=604480" title="">
                        New rental funding for regulated housing tenants in Trondheim
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development, 11.05.2010]</p>
                <p>Rental regulation for pre-war housing was phased out in the New Year. In a revised national budget, the Government issues a bill on new housing rental funding for occupants who are unable to pay current rents for such housing in Trondheim. This funding will be means-tested.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp546192885_wp1648794796_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl01_Label1"></span>                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/Styrer-rad-og-utvalg/Child-Welfare-Service-Conflict-Resolution-Board.html?id=589293" title="">
                        Child Welfare Service Conflict Resolution Board
                    </a>
                </h2>
